              "text": "## Canonical User Intent (already disambiguated by LLM)\r\nRepeat calling the goal 'WaitAndCheck' as long as the variable %continueWaiting% remains true\n## functions available starts ##\r\n{\"Description\":\"While, for, foreach, loops, repeat, go through a list and call a goal\",\"ExampleInformation\":\"Examples with methods first define an example plang code and then(=>) how it is mapped to parameters\",\"Methods\":[{\"Description\":\"Repeat a call to a function number of time. Great for pagination, where repeatCount is page count and startIndex is page number. startIndex starts at 0\",\"MethodName\":\"Repeat\",\"Parameters\":[{\"Type\":\"System.Int32\",\"Name\":\"repeatCounter\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"PLang.Models.GoalToCallInfo\",\"Name\":\"goalToCall\",\"Description\":\"(see Type information in SupportingObjects)\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Int32\",\"Name\":\"startIndex\",\"DefaultValue\":0,\"IsRequired\":false}]},{\"Description\":\"Predefined variables are %list%, %item%, %position%, %listCount%, user can overwrite those using parameters, e.g. `- go through %products%, call goal ProcessProduct item=%product%`, parameter key is \\\"item\\\" and value is \\\"%product%\\\". cpuUsage is percentage of cpu cores available, 80% => 0.8\",\"MethodName\":\"RunLoop\",\"Parameters\":[{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"variableToLoopThrough\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"PLang.Models.GoalToCallInfo\",\"Name\":\"goalToCall\",\"Description\":\"(see Type information in SupportingObjects)\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"PLang.Modules.LoopModule.Program+MultiThreaded\",\"Name\":\"multiThreaded\",\"Description\":\"(see Type information in SupportingObjects)\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"PLang.Modules.LoopModule.Program+LinqOptions\",\"Name\":\"linqOptions\",\"Description\":\"(see Type information in SupportingObjects)\",\"IsRequired\":false}]},{\"Description\":\"While loop - repeatedly calls a goal while a condition is true. The called goal can return variables to update the condition.\",\"MethodName\":\"While\",\"Parameters\":[{\"Type\":\"PLang.Modules.ConditionalModule.ConditionEvaluator+Condition\",\"Name\":\"condition\",\"Description\":\"(see Type information in SupportingObjects)\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"PLang.Models.GoalToCallInfo\",\"Name\":\"goalToCall\",\"Description\":\"(see Type information in SupportingObjects)\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Int32\",\"Name\":\"maxIterations\",\"DefaultValue\":10000,\"IsRequired\":false}],\"Examples\":[\"while %count% < 10, call goal IncrementCount => condition={Kind:Simple, LeftValue:%count%, Operator:\\\"<\\\", RightValue:10}, goalToCall={Name:\\\"IncrementCount\\\"}\",\"while %isRunning% is true, call goal CheckStatus => condition={Kind:Simple, LeftValue:%isRunning%, Operator:\\\"==\\\", RightValue:true}, goalToCall={Name:\\\"CheckStatus\\\"}\",\"while %response% is empty, call goal WaitForResponse => condition={Kind:Simple, LeftValue:%response%, Operator:\\\"isEmpty\\\"}, goalToCall={Name:\\\"WaitForResponse\\\"}\"]}],\"SupportingObjects\":[{\"Type\":\"PLang.Models.GoalToCallInfo\",\"Name\":\"goalToCall\",\"Description\":\"Name of goal and parameters that is called, e.g. in condition, loops, run goal. Keep Name as user defines it with path\",\"TypeProperties\":[{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"Name\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`2[System.String,System.Object]\",\"Name\":\"Parameters\",\"Description\":\"Name of goal and parameters that is called, e.g. in condition, loops, run goal. Keep Name as user defines it with path\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Boolean\",\"Name\":\"WaitForExecution\",\"Description\":\"Whether to wait for the goal to complete before continuing. Default is true.\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Int64\",\"Name\":\"DelayWhenNotWaitingInMilliseconds\",\"Description\":\"Delay in milliseconds when not waiting for execution. Default is 50.\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.UInt32\",\"Name\":\"WaitForXMillisecondsBeforeRunningGoal\",\"Description\":\"Wait for X milliseconds before running the goal. Default is 0.\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Boolean\",\"Name\":\"Isolated\",\"Description\":\"Run the goal in an isolated container. Default is false.\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Boolean\",\"Name\":\"DisableSystemGoals\",\"Description\":\"Disable system/OS goals when running. Default is false.\",\"IsRequired\":true}],\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"PLang.Modules.LoopModule.Program+MultiThreaded\",\"Name\":\"multiThreaded\",\"TypeProperties\":[{\"Type\":\"System.Int32\",\"Name\":\"ThreadCount\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Double\",\"Name\":\"CpuUsage\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Boolean\",\"Name\":\"FailFast\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"PLang.Models.GoalToCallInfo\",\"Name\":\"GoalToCallBeforeItemIsProcessed\",\"Description\":\"(see PLang.Models.GoalToCallInfo type information in SupportingObjects)\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"PLang.Models.GoalToCallInfo\",\"Name\":\"GoalToCallAfterItemIsProcessed\",\"Description\":\"(see PLang.Models.GoalToCallInfo type information in SupportingObjects)\",\"IsRequired\":false}],\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"PLang.Modules.LoopModule.Program+LinqOptions\",\"Name\":\"linqOptions\",\"TypeProperties\":[{\"Type\":\"System.Int32\",\"Name\":\"Split\",\"IsRequired\":true}],\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"PLang.Modules.ConditionalModule.ConditionEvaluator+Condition\",\"Name\":\"condition\",\"TypeProperties\":[{\"Type\":\"PLang.Modules.ConditionalModule.ConditionEvaluator+ConditionKind\",\"Name\":\"Kind\",\"AvailableValues\":\"Simple|Compound\",\"IsRequired\":true},{\"Type\":\"System.Object\",\"Name\":\"LeftValue\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.String\",\"Name\":\"Operator\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"System.Object\",\"Name\":\"RightValue\",\"IsRequired\":false},{\"Type\":\"Sy